</section>

<p class="ea-compare__caption">
  Same function. <strong>5 seconds to grok</strong>, not 5 minutes and your CI
  catches it the moment someone removes <code>AuditLog</code> or swaps <code
    >sequential</code
  > for <code>parallel</code>.
</p>
